snippet.title: Office Management 101 - Alpha teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Play the free Alpha Demo on Itch.io now!
https://tulevikeu.itch.io/office-management-101

Wishlist and follow on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/678390/Office_Management_101/

Office Management 101 is a satirical office life simulation tycoon game set in a fictional capitalistic dystopia. Step over competitors, drive your staff to the limit and milk your customers for every penny in the pursuit of spiraling success!

http://officemanagement101.com/

Game developed by tulevik.EU

Music by Theo Cranmore https://soundcloud.com/theocranmore
Trailer art and animation by Uku Randver
